Esperanto--English
==================================================================

You need apertium-3.1 and lttoolbox-3.1 to use this translator,
as well as the cg-proc utility (see http://beta.visl.sdu.dk/cg3/chunked/index.html
and especially chapter 3 "Installation & Updating").

To compile the linguistic data simply do:

./configure       (or sh autogen.sh if you have downloaded from SVN)
make
make install

inside of this directory.

Further documentation is available in the README and at: 

 http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/English_and_Esperanto

===================================================================

More information about this module, and others can be found on
the Apertium: Wiki, http://wiki.apertium.org


